SUMMARY:Riichi Mahjong
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nThe RIICHI Mahjong group meets on Monday
 s at 6:30 pm at:\nGiant Supermarket\n2300 Linglestown Rd.\nHarrisburg\, PA
  17110\n\nLight refreshments.\nBeginners welcome.\nThis is real Mah with t
 iles.
