SUMMARY:(H.B.G.) - Harrisburg Board Gaming 
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nCome to game night in the Harrisburg are
 a! Every 2nd and 4th Friday of every month\, there will be gaming at the L
 ife Point Church. Event starts at 6:00pm in the Churches Lobby / Sitting A
 rea and goes until you're too tired to play anymore.\n\nFeel Free to bring
  your own games\, food and drinks! We have a kitchen available to be used 
 and a Fridge for your drinks. Come check us out.\n\nJon Krehling is the or
 ganizer of this event\, so message him on meetup if you have any questions
 !
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/events/308160865/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250530T160144Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250530T160144Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
