SUMMARY:Dillsburg Game Night - 24 Hour Board Game Day - Extra Life/CMN
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nEvery year\, we host a fundraiser for th
 e Children’s Miracle Network / Extra Life\, and this year everything beg
 ins at 8 a.m. on Saturday\, April 11\, and winds down at 8 a.m. on Sunday\
 , April 12.\n\nOur goal is to raise $3\,000. There will be plenty of chanc
 es to donate during the event\, and you can also make a contribution here.
 \n\nWe have a TON of fun events planned. Some highlights:\n\nLife-Size Hot
  Streak – Costumes! Mayhem! Insanity! And you can bet on it!\n\nMarble R
 ace – Make a donation\, name your marbles and compete for a copy of Thun
 der Road: Vendetta and other great prizes.\n\nPlay2Win – An easy chance 
 to learn and win great games like Euphoria\, Fromage\, Sides\, Tokaido Duo
 \, Yinsh\, Zooloretto\, and more.\n\nGame Auction – So many great games\
 , including a few hard-to-find promos\, will be sold to the highest bidder
 !\n\nChaos Dominion – If you like Dominion\, you’re going to LOVE Chao
 s Dominion.\n\nBlood on the Clocktower – The brilliant social deduction 
 game.\n\nSo many more games… And of course please bring your own!\n\nBre
 akfast\, lunch & pizza dinner for all participantsz\n\nCheck our Event Pag
 e on Facebook for more details.\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/share/1GHNfptf
 a7/?mibextid=wwXIfr
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/events/314092196/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260402T180818Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260402T180818Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
