SUMMARY:2nd Saturday Gaming - Colonial Park United Church of Christ
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\n**COVID Notice**\nIf you are fully vacci
 nated\, no mask is required. If not\, you are required by the church to we
 ar a face mask. If you're not vacced and not willing to wear a mask then p
 lease do not attend.\n\nhttp://www.centralpagameclub.com/images/entrance.j
 pg\n\nCard and board games covering a huge gamut of themes - anything from
  developing islands\, staging cruises\, casting movies\, to building railr
 oads. There are themes appealing to every audience and most games play in 
 45-90 minutes. Our friendly members are happy to teach. Many games are beg
 inner-friendly and can be taught in about 10 minutes.\n\nAdults 16 & older
 .\n\nNewcomers are welcome.\n\nVisit http://www.centralpagameclub.com for 
 more information.\n\nWhen you enter the church's parking lot\, park in the
  back\, come in through the courtyard\, and look for the door in the pictu
 re above.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/events/313895806/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260322T150047Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T150047Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
